let p1 = new Promise((resolve,reject) => resolve(17));
p1.then((v) => console.log(v)); // first reaction, prints 17
p1.then((v) => console.log(v*2)); // second reaction, prints 34
p1.then((v) => console.log(v*3)); // third reaction, prints 51
